{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbdb6868a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6631"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6631"},"text":"§ 6631.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Establishment of Committee","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The President shall establish within the Executive Office of the President a President’s Committee on Science and Technology (hereinafter referred to as the “Committee”).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbdb6868b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/282/tIII/s301"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–282, title III, § 301","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-05-11"},"text":"May 11, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/468"},"text":"90 Stat. 468","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbdb6868c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"idbdb6868d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idbdb6868e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Abolition of President’s Committee on Science and Technology; Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The President’s Committee on Science and Technology, established pursuant to this subchapter, was abolished and its functions transferred to the President, by Reorg. Plan No. 1 of 1977, § 5A, 42 F.R. 56101, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/91/1634"},"text":"91 Stat. 1634","children":[],"tail":", set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees, effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-02-26"},"text":"Feb. 26, 1978","children":[],"tail":", as provided by section 1(b) of Ex. Ord. No. 12039, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-02-24"},"text":"Feb. 24, 1978","children":[],"tail":", 43 F.R. 8095, set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s6601"},"text":"section 6601 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
